MBIA, Merrill Agree to Dismiss Mortgage-Debt Protection Suit

-- B y   M i c h a e l   H y t h a
-- 
2011-07-11T23:19:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/mbia-merrill-lynch-agree-to-dismiss-suit-over-mortgage-debt-protection.html
Merrill Lynch & Co. units now owned
by  Bank of America Corp. (BAC)  and  MBIA Inc. (MBI)  agreed to dismiss a
breach-of-contract lawsuit over protection sold against
mortgage-debt defaults, according to a filing in New York state
court.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at 
 mhytha@bloomberg.net  